<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="th">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>ค้นหารายชื่อผู้สมัครเพื่อรายงานตัว - โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</title>
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Sarabun:wght@300;400;500;600;700&family=Noto+Serif+Thai:wght@400;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        :root {
            --primary: #1a2744;
            --primary-light: #243460;
            --accent: #c9a84c;
            --accent-light: #f0d98a;
            --surface: #ffffff;
            --surface-2: #f4f3ef;
            --border: #e2ddd4;
            --text: #1a2744;
            --text-muted: #8a8070;
            --error: #c0392b;
        }

        * { margin: 0; padding: 0; box-sizing: border-box; }

        html, body {
            height: 100%;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            background: var(--primary);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            min-height: 100vh;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        /* Background decoration */
        body::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background:
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 20% 50%, rgba(201,168,76,0.12) 0%, transparent 55%),
                radial-gradient(ellipse at 80% 20%, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 0%, transparent 50%),
                repeating-linear-gradient(
                    -45deg,
                    transparent,
                    transparent 60px,
                    rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 60px,
                    rgba(255,255,255,0.012) 120px
                );
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        /* Floating decorative circles */
        .bg-circle {
            position: absolute;
            border-radius: 50%;
            pointer-events: none;
        }
        .bg-circle-1 {
            width: 500px; height: 500px;
            top: -180px; right: -120px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(201,168,76,0.07) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }
        .bg-circle-2 {
            width: 400px; height: 400px;
            bottom: -150px; left: -100px;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(255,255,255,0.04) 0%, transparent 70%);
        }

        /* ===== CARD ===== */
        .card {
            background: var(--surface);
            border-radius: 24px;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 480px;
            margin: 24px;
            box-shadow:
                0 32px 80px rgba(0,0,0,0.35),
                0 0 0 1px rgba(255,255,255,0.06);
            overflow: hidden;
            position: relative;
            animation: cardIn 0.6s cubic-bezier(0.22, 1, 0.36, 1) both;
        }

        @keyframes cardIn {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(32px) scale(0.97); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0) scale(1); }
        }

        /* Card top banner */
        .card-banner {
            background: var(--primary);
            padding: 32px 36px 28px;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
        }

        .card-banner::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            bottom: 0; left: 0; right: 0;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, var(--accent) 0%, var(--accent-light) 60%, transparent 100%);
        }

        .banner-deco {
            position: absolute;
            right: -20px; top: -20px;
            width: 130px; height: 130px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 28px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.08);
        }

        .banner-deco-2 {
            position: absolute;
            right: 40px; bottom: -30px;
            width: 80px; height: 80px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 18px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.05);
        }

        .school-logo {
            width: 52px; height: 52px;
            background: rgba(201,168,76,0.15);
            border: 1.5px solid rgba(201,168,76,0.4);
            border-radius: 14px;
            display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            margin-bottom: 16px;
        }

        .school-logo svg {
            width: 26px; height: 26px;
            fill: none;
            stroke: var(--accent);
            stroke-width: 1.8;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
        }

        .school-name {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.4;
        }

        .school-sub {
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: rgba(255,255,255,0.45);
            margin-top: 4px;
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
        }

        /* Card body */
        .card-body {
            padding: 32px 36px 36px;
        }

        .section-title {
            font-family: 'Noto Serif Thai', serif;
            font-size: 1.25rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            margin-bottom: 6px;
        }

        .section-desc {
            font-size: 0.875rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-bottom: 28px;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        /* Input group */
        .input-group {
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .input-label {
            display: block;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            font-weight: 700;
            color: var(--text);
            letter-spacing: 0.06em;
            text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .input-wrapper {
            position: relative;
        }

        .input-icon {
            position: absolute;
            left: 16px;
            top: 50%;
            transform: translateY(-50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .input-icon svg {
            width: 18px; height: 18px;
            stroke: var(--text-muted);
            stroke-width: 1.8;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            fill: none;
            display: block;
            transition: stroke 0.2s;
        }

        input[type="text"] {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 14px 16px 14px 48px;
            border: 1.5px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            color: var(--text);
            background: var(--surface-2);
            transition: border-color 0.2s, box-shadow 0.2s, background 0.2s;
            outline: none;
            letter-spacing: 0.05em;
        }

        input[type="text"]::placeholder {
            color: #b8b2a8;
            letter-spacing: 0;
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus {
            border-color: var(--accent);
            background: #fff;
            box-shadow: 0 0 0 4px rgba(201,168,76,0.12);
        }

        input[type="text"]:focus ~ .input-icon svg,
        .input-wrapper:focus-within .input-icon svg {
            stroke: var(--accent);
        }

        /* Error message */
        .error-msg {
            display: none;
            font-size: 0.8rem;
            color: var(--error);
            margin-top: 8px;
            padding-left: 4px;
            animation: shake 0.3s ease;
        }

        .error-msg.show { display: block; }

        @keyframes shake {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
            25% { transform: translateX(-6px); }
            75% { transform: translateX(6px); }
        }

        /* Button */
        .btn-search {
            width: 100%;
            padding: 15px;
            background: var(--primary);
            color: #fff;
            border: none;
            border-radius: 12px;
            font-family: 'Sarabun', sans-serif;
            font-size: 1rem;
            font-weight: 600;
            cursor: pointer;
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            gap: 10px;
            transition: background 0.2s, transform 0.15s, box-shadow 0.2s;
            position: relative;
            overflow: hidden;
            letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        }

        .btn-search::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, rgba(201,168,76,0.18) 0%, transparent 60%);
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.2s;
        }

        .btn-search:hover {
            background: var(--primary-light);
            transform: translateY(-1px);
            box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(26,39,68,0.25);
        }

        .btn-search:hover::before { opacity: 1; }

        .btn-search:active {
            transform: translateY(0);
            box-shadow: none;
        }

        .btn-search svg {
            width: 18px; height: 18px;
            stroke: currentColor;
            stroke-width: 2;
            fill: none;
            stroke-linecap: round;
            stroke-linejoin: round;
            flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        /* Divider */
        .divider {
            height: 1px;
            background: var(--border);
            margin: 24px 0;
        }

        /* Footer note */
        .card-footer-note {
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 0.78rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .card-footer-note a {
            color: var(--primary);
            font-weight: 600;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        /* Press Enter hint */
        .enter-hint {
            display: inline-flex;
            align-items: center;
            gap: 5px;
            font-size: 0.72rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
            margin-top: 10px;
            opacity: 0;
            transition: opacity 0.3s;
        }

        .enter-hint.visible { opacity: 1; }

        .key-badge {
            background: var(--surface-2);
            border: 1px solid var(--border);
            border-radius: 4px;
            padding: 1px 6px;
            font-family: monospace;
            font-size: 0.7rem;
            color: var(--text-muted);
        }

        @media (max-width: 520px) {
            .card-banner, .card-body { padding-left: 24px; padding-right: 24px; }
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

    <div class="bg-circle bg-circle-1"></div>
    <div class="bg-circle bg-circle-2"></div>

    <div class="card">

        <!-- Banner -->
        <div class="card-banner">
            <div class="banner-deco"></div>
            <div class="banner-deco-2"></div>

            <div class="school-logo">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <path d="M3 9.5L12 4l9 5.5V20H3V9.5z"/>
                    <path d="M9 20v-6h6v6"/>
                    <path d="M12 4v3M8 7h8"/>
                </svg>
            </div>

            <div class="school-name">โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา</div>
            <div class="school-sub">Oraphim Wittaya School &nbsp;·&nbsp; ระบบรายงานตัวนักเรียน</div>
        </div>

        <!-- Body -->
        <div class="card-body">
            <h2 class="section-title">ค้นหาข้อมูลผู้สมัคร</h2>
            <p class="section-desc">กรอกรหัสประจำตัวผู้สมัครเพื่อดำเนินการรายงานตัวเข้าเป็นนักเรียน</p>

            <div class="input-group">
                <label class="input-label" for="id">รหัสประจำตัวผู้สมัคร</label>
                <div class="input-wrapper">
                    <div class="input-icon">
                        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                            <rect x="3" y="4" width="18" height="16" rx="2"/>
                            <circle cx="9" cy="10" r="2"/>
                            <path d="M15 8h2M15 12h2M7 16h10"/>
                        </svg>
                    </div>
                    <input
                        type="text"
                        id="id"
                        name="id"
                        placeholder="XXXX"
                        oninput="this.value = this.value.replace(/[^0-9]/g, ''); onInput()"
                        onkeydown="if(event.key==='Enter') search()"
                        maxlength="10"
                        autocomplete="off"
                        required
                    >
                </div>
                <span class="enter-hint" id="enterHint">
                    กด <span class="key-badge">Enter</span> หรือปุ่มค้นหาด้านล่าง
                </span>
                <div class="error-msg" id="errorMsg">⚠ กรุณากรอกรหัสประจำตัวผู้สมัครก่อน</div>
            </div>

            <button class="btn-search" onclick="search()">
                <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24">
                    <circle cx="11" cy="11" r="7"/>
                    <path d="M21 21l-4.35-4.35"/>
                </svg>
                ค้นหาและรายงานตัว
            </button>

            <div class="divider"></div>

            <p class="card-footer-note">
                หากไม่พบข้อมูลหรือมีปัญหา กรุณาติดต่อเจ้าหน้าที่<br>
                ห้องทะเบียน โรงเรียนอรพิมพ์วิทยา
            </p>
        </div>

    </div>

    <script>
        function onInput() {
            const val = document.querySelector('#id').value;
            const hint = document.getElementById('enterHint');
            const err  = document.getElementById('errorMsg');
            hint.classList.toggle('visible', val.length > 0);
            if (val.length > 0) err.classList.remove('show');
        }

        function search() {
            const idDom = document.querySelector('#id');
            const id = idDom.value.trim();

            if (!id) {
                const err = document.getElementById('errorMsg');
                err.classList.remove('show');
                void err.offsetWidth; // re-trigger animation
                err.classList.add('show');
                idDom.focus();
                return;
            }

            window.open('/reporting/' + id);
        }
    </script>

</body>
</html>